name: OrderedPropertiesTest
description: Unit tests for the OrderedProperties class, focusing on various operations like compute, merge, put, and remove.

test_cases.name: testCompute
test_cases.description: Tests the compute functionality of OrderedProperties, ensuring keys and values are computed and ordered correctly.

test_cases.name: testComputeIfAbsent
test_cases.description: Tests the computeIfAbsent functionality of OrderedProperties, ensuring keys and values are computed if absent and ordered correctly.

test_cases.name: testEntrySet
test_cases.description: Tests the entrySet functionality of OrderedProperties, ensuring entries are iterated and ordered correctly.

test_cases.name: testForEach
test_cases.description: Tests the forEach functionality of OrderedProperties, ensuring keys and values are iterated and ordered correctly.

test_cases.name: testKeys
test_cases.description: Tests the keys functionality of OrderedProperties, ensuring keys are iterated and ordered correctly.

test_cases.name: testLoadOrderedKeys
test_cases.description: Tests the load functionality of OrderedProperties, ensuring properties are loaded from a file and ordered correctly.

test_cases.name: testLoadOrderedKeysReverse
test_cases.description: Tests the load functionality of OrderedProperties, ensuring properties are loaded from a file in reverse order and ordered correctly.

test_cases.name: testMerge
test_cases.description: Tests the merge functionality of OrderedProperties, ensuring keys and values are merged and ordered correctly.

test_cases.name: testPut
test_cases.description: Tests the put functionality of OrderedProperties, ensuring keys and values are added and ordered correctly.

test_cases.name: testPutAll
test_cases.description: Tests the putAll functionality of OrderedProperties, ensuring all keys and values from a map are added and ordered correctly.

test_cases.name: testPutIfAbsent
test_cases.description: Tests the putIfAbsent functionality of OrderedProperties, ensuring keys and values are added if absent and ordered correctly.

test_cases.name: testRemoveKey
test_cases.description: Tests the remove functionality of OrderedProperties, ensuring a key is removed and does not exist in the properties.

test_cases.name: testRemoveKeyValue
test_cases.description: Tests the remove functionality of OrderedProperties, ensuring a key-value pair is removed and does not exist in the properties.

test_cases.name: testToString
test_cases.description: Tests the toString functionality of OrderedProperties, ensuring the string representation is correct and ordered.
